// ── VIAL KEYBOARD UID ─────────────────────────────────────────────
// A unique 8-byte identifier for this keyboard in Vial's database.
// This ID is embedded in the firmware so Vial can identify the keyboard
// without needing an internet connection or a server lookup.
//
// IMPORTANT: Never reuse this UID across different keyboards.
// If you fork this keyboard definition for a new design, regenerate
